{
  "stem": "26728.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then you had-- they left you in there for another 48 hours if you weren't dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the idea of that today frightens me just to think of being put in a place like that and left there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you can't move, you can't raise your arm to scratch your head or nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You just stand there until they let you out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you can't see, you can't hear, and you can't-- a total-- that is the-- that's the cruelty that I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And The Other things they did at Mauthausen, they called it parachuting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They take these Jews to the-- and they were really-- and they did a lot of medical experimentation at Mauthausen, too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I've seen evidence of that since the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I saw it then too, but they had a doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They didn't have Mengele, but they had one just like him who had a thing about dwarfs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they would kill dwarfs, and they liked to do families, a family that maybe some of them might have two or three dwarfs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I'm not talking about midgets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'm talking about dwarfs who are just-- who are, you know, uh, not properly formed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They have real short arms, whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They would kill them, boil them until all the flesh was gone, and then these doctors would try to figure out why-- what it was that made them be dwarfs.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they had skeletons of these dwarfs there in this-- at Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Unreal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I mean - you know, It was just unreal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The parachuting was where they take them-- Mauthausen was in a big quarry, and it was designed this way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were 176 steps, I believe, from the top of the quarry to the bottom, and they were uneven so that you couldn't just walk down steps.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
